++	// multiply [H^(i+1), H^i] by [H^2, H^2] to get [H^(i+3), H^(i+2)].
++	// With VL=64, repeatedly multiply [H^(i+3), H^(i+2), H^(i+1), H^i] by
++	// [H^4, H^4, H^4, H^4] to get [H^(i+7), H^(i+6), H^(i+5), H^(i+4)].
