++ * compression level, the same as in a normal compression operation.
++ *
++ * The user shall instruct zstd to use a particular ZSTD_sequenceProducer_F
++ * function by calling
++ *         ZSTD_registerSequenceProducer(cctx,
++ *                                       sequenceProducerState,
++ *                                       sequenceProducer)
